title: Naomi Scott Cast As Pink Ranger For New Power Rangers Movie
text: Naomi Scott Cast As Pink Ranger For New Power Rangers Movie Reported by Jay Cochran - 2015.10.08 Lionsgate has announced that actress Naomi Scott (The Martian) has been cast as the Pink Power Ranger for the upcoming Power Rangers reboot movie. Lionsgate' Power Rangers will open during Martin Luther King Jr. weekend 2017, on January 13th.
